[Skin metastasis as first manifestation of prostatic adenocarcinoma].

[Article in Spanish]

Gallego Sánchez JA(1), Astobieta Odriozola A, Alvarez Martínez J, Ibarlucea 
González JG, Larrinaga Simón J, Bernuy Malfaz C.

