locus in male but not in female centenarians with respect to matched controls. 
On the other hand no significant difference was found between case/control 
genotypic frequencies at REN, PARP, SOD2 loci. The latter loci therefore do not 
affect inter-individual variability in life expectancy (at least in terms of 
qualitative variants associated with the tested markers). However, the data is 
consistent with an association between the THO locus and longevity.

